Package enteties

Class TestToExecute

  • java.lang.Object
    • enteties.TestToExecute
  • public class TestToExecute
extends java.lang.Object
    The TestToExecute class represents a test to be executed. It contains various properties related to the test, such as test code, test ID, testing type, date, average, median, lock, time extension, and more. The class also provides methods to get and set these properties. Additionally, it includes methods for creating JavaFX UI components like CheckBox, RadioButton, Button, ComboBox, and TextField.
